Package com.tangosol.config.expression

Class SystemPropertyParameterResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tangosol.config.expression.SystemPropertyParameterResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterResolver
    public class SystemPropertyParameterResolver
extends Object
implements ParameterResolver
    A SystemPropertyParameterResolver is a ParameterResolver that is based on property methods on System.

    Replaces {@link com.tangosol.config.expression.PropertiesParameterResolver(java.util.Map)} since it required read and write access for all Properties for simple property access. resolve(String) only requires read access for property specified.

    Since:
    Coherence 12.2.1
    Author:
    jf 2015.04.15
